1889 cabinet of the Cardenas team who played a portion of the year in the Cuban Pro league and then withdrew never to be heard from again.  Photo features a 16 year old Esteban Prats who would go on to star in the Cuban league for twenty years and also play in the minors in the US
Photo has some rough spots and contrast is a bit light- there is some tracing of the players- but this may be the earliest in uniform outside Cuban baseball image ( there was a 1886 image in rea that was an out of uniform studio shot 


Image is about 7.5x4.25
Asking 400 delivered

350 delivered 

Please note I will not be going lower and will be putting back in my collection if it doesn’t sell
Hi, besides Pratt can you read the rest of the names as they are not legible on the photo.   thank you, claudio
